_:N88ca882abca34c4c90bcc40bf34e8047 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Greg Jackson is a British entrepreneur and <abbr title=\"Chief Executive Officer\">CEO</abbr> of Octopus Energy which he founded in 2015, one of the largest energy firms in the UK. Before Octopus Energy, Greg was an entrepreneur with experience in various sectors including mirror manufacturing, coffee shops and software. Before turning aged 30 years, he had owned or managed a number of <abbr title=\"small and medium-sized enterprises\">SMEs</abbr>. He is an investor and advisor in several tech startups. In 2024 he was awarded a <abbr title=\"Commander of the Most Excellent Order of the British Empire\">CBE</abbr> for services to the energy industry.</p>\n\n" .
